title: Endgame stats
body:
So this happened to me before...
____
Anyone ever experience this?

replies.body:
>**115 mynoots

I'm sorry, I just died of laughter.

Does this happen to you regularly?
Nope, first time. And I know, I lost it when I read it also.

Well, I for one call tell you that I've never seen this before. Could have been a result of a really quick drop in internet data.

We'll never know for sure, though.

~~noot noot~~

Ah Pingu, you never fail to amuse me.

Issue has not occurred again so I would say this has been resolved.

Thanks.
As Horse Of Force said your internet did not get the end game data in what would be considered a reasonable amount of time and thus  there was nothing to display.
